text: Skinner Jones, (born on October 24, 1996 in Tennessee, United States), is a American professional model and internet celebrity in California. He moved to Los Angeles from Dickson, Tennesee.https://www.mycast.io/talent/skinner-jones ==Modeling career== He is under contract in Adon Magazine and Wilhelmina model agency in the United States. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:American people Category:American models Category:American Internet celebrities
